        <briefdescription>
<para>Constructs a polygon that is the locus of points at a distance less than or equal to a specified distance from this geometry. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>source</parametername>
